name: Food Delivery
description:
Life of a food courier isn't easy. Grab some vegetables and try to match up them to orders. Try not to mistake orders and drive safely until the day is off. You've got 2 minutes.

1. Check what customers in houses wants.

2. Gather food from one of 3 factories.

3. Deliver food to appropriate house.

Use arrow keys to control a car.

HAVE FUN!

@LukasTkacz
